        <updateDate>2015-02-23T20:09:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Medicare Residential Care Coordination Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> Directs the Secretary of Health and Human Services to establish and implement a demonstration project under titles XVIII (Medicare) and XIX (Medicaid) of the Social Security Act to evaluate the use of capitated payments made to eligible continuing care retirement communities for residential care coordination programs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
